4. **Sequential Command Structure**: Organize commands so that each step relies on the successful completion of the previous one, ensuring a smooth workflow.
5. **Documentation and Logging**: Keep a record of actions taken and their outcomes to identify patterns in unresponsiveness or failure, which can help in troubleshooting.
